PRELIMINARY EARTHQUAKE PARAMETERS
---------------------------------
 
  * MAGNITUDE      7.0
  * ORIGIN TIME    2141 UTC JUL 27 2015
  * COORDINATES    2.8 SOUTH  138.6 EAST
  * DEPTH          33 KM / 20 MILES
  * LOCATION       PAPUA  INDONESIA
 

EVALUATION
----------
 
  * AN EARTHQUAKE WITH A PRELIMINARY MAGNITUDE OF 7.0 OCCURRED IN
    PAPUA, INDONESIA AT 2141 UTC ON MONDAY JULY 27 2015.
 
  * BASED ON ALL AVAILABLE DATA... THERE IS NO TSUNAMI THREAT
    FROM THIS EARTHQUAKE.
 

RECOMMENDED ACTIONS
-------------------
 
  * NO ACTION IS REQUIRED.
 

